#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.23:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "3. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Kāyasutta"
msgstr "23. Body"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.39"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:1.1"
msgid "“Atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā kāyena pahātabbā, no vācāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are things that should be given up by the body, not by "
"speech."

msgctxt "an10.23:1.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā vācāya pahātabbā, no kāyena."
msgstr "There are things that should be given up by speech, not by the body."

#. VAR: paññāya disvā → disvā disvā (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.23:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā neva kāyena pahātabbā no vācāya, paññāya disvā "
"pahātabbā."
msgstr ""
"There are things that should be given up neither by the body, nor by speech, "
"but by seeing again and again with wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:2.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā kāyena pahātabbā, no vācāya?"
msgstr ""
"And what are the things that should be given up by the body, not by speech?"

#. VAR: āpanno hoti kiñci desaṃ → kañcideva desaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an10.23:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akusalaṃ āpanno hoti kiñci desaṃ kāyena."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has committed a certain unskillful offense by way of "
"body."

msgctxt "an10.23:2.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ anuvicca viññū sabrahmacārī evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "After examination, sensible spiritual companions say this to them:"

msgctxt "an10.23:2.4"
msgid "‘āyasmā kho akusalaṃ āpanno kiñci desaṃ kāyena."
msgstr ""
"‘Venerable, you’ve committed a certain unskillful offense by way of body."

msgctxt "an10.23:2.5"
msgid "Sādhu vatāyasmā kāyaduccaritaṃ pahāya kāyasucaritaṃ bhāvetū’ti."
msgstr ""
"Please give up that bad bodily conduct and develop good bodily conduct.’"

msgctxt "an10.23:2.6"
msgid ""
"So anuvicca viññūhi sabrahmacārīhi vuccamāno kāyaduccaritaṃ pahāya "
"kāyasucaritaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"When spoken to by their sensible spiritual companions they give up that bad "
"bodily conduct and develop good bodily conduct."

msgctxt "an10.23:2.7"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā kāyena pahātabbā, no vācāya."
msgstr ""
"These are the things that should be given up by the body, not by speech."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:3.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā vācāya pahātabbā, no kāyena?"
msgstr ""
"And what are the things that should be given up by speech, not by the body?"

msgctxt "an10.23:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akusalaṃ āpanno hoti kiñci desaṃ vācāya."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has committed a certain unskillful offense by way of "
"speech."

msgctxt "an10.23:3.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ anuvicca viññū sabrahmacārī evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "After examination, sensible spiritual companions say this to them:"

msgctxt "an10.23:3.4"
msgid "‘āyasmā kho akusalaṃ āpanno kiñci desaṃ vācāya."
msgstr ""
"‘Venerable, you’ve committed a certain unskillful offense by way of speech."

msgctxt "an10.23:3.5"
msgid "Sādhu vatāyasmā vacīduccaritaṃ pahāya vacīsucaritaṃ bhāvetū’ti."
msgstr ""
"Please give up that bad verbal conduct and develop good verbal conduct.’"

msgctxt "an10.23:3.6"
msgid ""
"So anuvicca viññūhi sabrahmacārīhi vuccamāno vacīduccaritaṃ pahāya "
"vacīsucaritaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"When spoken to by their sensible spiritual companions they give up that bad "
"verbal conduct and develop good verbal conduct."

msgctxt "an10.23:3.7"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā vācāya pahātabbā, no kāyena."
msgstr ""
"These are the things that should be given up by speech, not by the body."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.40"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:4.1"
msgid ""
"Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā neva kāyena pahātabbā no vācāya, paññāya disvā "
"pahātabbā?"
msgstr ""
"And what are the things that should be given up neither by the body, nor by "
"speech, but by seeing again and again with wisdom?"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.2"
msgid ""
"Lobho, bhikkhave, neva kāyena pahātabbo no vācāya, paññāya disvā pahātabbo."
msgstr "Greed …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.3"
msgid "Doso, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "hate …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.4"
msgid "moho …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.5"
msgid "kodho …"
msgstr "anger …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.6"
msgid "upanāho …"
msgstr "hostility …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.7"
msgid "makkho …"
msgstr "offensiveness …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.8"
msgid "paḷāso …"
msgstr "contempt …"

msgctxt "an10.23:4.9"
msgid ""
"macchariyaṃ, bhikkhave, neva kāyena pahātabbaṃ no vācāya, paññāya disvā "
"pahātabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"and stinginess are things that should be given up neither by the body, nor "
"by speech, but by seeing again and again with wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:5.1"
msgid ""
"Pāpikā, bhikkhave, issā neva kāyena pahātabbā no vācāya, paññāya disvā "
"pahātabbā."
msgstr ""
"Nasty jealousy should be given up neither by the body, nor by speech, but by "
"seeing again and again with wisdom."

msgctxt "an10.23:5.2"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, pāpikā issā?"
msgstr "And what is nasty jealousy?"

msgctxt "an10.23:5.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ijjhati gahapatissa vā gahapatiputtassa vā dhanena vā "
"dhaññena vā rajatena vā jātarūpena vā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a householder or their child is prospering in money, grain, "
"silver, or gold."

msgctxt "an10.23:5.4"
msgid "Tatrāññatarassa dāsassa vā upavāsassa vā evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "And a bondservant or dependent thinks:"

msgctxt "an10.23:5.5"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatimassa gahapatissa vā gahapatiputtassa vā na ijjheyya dhanena vā "
"dhaññena vā rajatena vā jātarūpena vā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, may that householder or their child not prosper in money, grain, "
"silver, or gold!’"

msgctxt "an10.23:5.6"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo vā pana brāhmaṇo vā lābhī hoti "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Or an ascetic or brahmin receives robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines "
"and supplies for the sick."

msgctxt "an10.23:5.7"
msgid "Tatrāññatarassa samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "And some other ascetic or brahmin thinks:"

msgctxt "an10.23:5.8"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata ayamāyasmā na lābhī assa "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, may that ascetic or brahmin not receive robes, alms-food, lodgings, and "
"medicines and supplies for the sick.’"

msgctxt "an10.23:5.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpikā issā."
msgstr "This is called nasty jealousy."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.41"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:6.1"
msgid ""
"Pāpikā, bhikkhave, icchā neva kāyena pahātabbā no vācāya, paññāya disvā "
"pahātabbā."
msgstr ""
"Corrupt wishes should be given up neither by the body, nor by speech, but by "
"seeing again and again with wisdom."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.2"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, pāpikā icchā?"
msgstr "And what are corrupt wishes?"

msgctxt "an10.23:6.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco assaddho samāno ‘saddhoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "It’s when a faithless person wishes to be known as faithful."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.4"
msgid "dussīlo samāno ‘sīlavāti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "An unethical person wishes to be known as ethical."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.5"
msgid "appassuto samāno ‘bahussutoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "An uneducated person wishes to be known as learned."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.6"
msgid "saṅgaṇikārāmo samāno ‘pavivittoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "A lover of company wishes to be known as secluded."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.7"
msgid "kusīto samāno ‘āraddhavīriyoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "A lazy person wishes to be known as energetic."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.8"
msgid "muṭṭhassati samāno ‘upaṭṭhitassatīti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "An unmindful person wishes to be known as mindful."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.9"
msgid "asamāhito samāno ‘samāhitoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "A person without immersion wishes to be known as having immersion."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.10"
msgid "duppañño samāno ‘paññavāti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati;"
msgstr "A witless person wishes to be known as wise."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.11"
msgid "akhīṇāsavo samāno ‘khīṇāsavoti maṃ jāneyyun’ti icchati."
msgstr ""
"A person who has not ended the defilements wishes to be known as having "
"ended the defilements."

msgctxt "an10.23:6.12"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpikā icchā."
msgstr "These are called corrupt wishes."

# Most manuscripts, followed PTS and BB, have this reading.
msgctxt "an10.23:6.13"
msgid ""
"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā neva kāyena pahātabbā no vācāya, paññāya "
"disvā pahātabbā."
msgstr ""
"Corrupt wishes should be given up neither by the body, nor by speech, but by "
"seeing again and again with wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:7.1"
msgid "Tañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuṃ lobho abhibhuyya iriyati, "
msgstr "Suppose that greed masters that mendicant and keeps going. "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.2"
msgid "doso …"
msgstr "Or that hate …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.3"
msgid "moho …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.4"
msgid "kodho …"
msgstr "anger …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.5"
msgid "upanāho …"
msgstr "hostility …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.6"
msgid "makkho …"
msgstr "offensiveness …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.7"
msgid "paḷāso …"
msgstr "contempt …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.8"
msgid "macchariyaṃ …"
msgstr "stinginess …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.9"
msgid "pāpikā issā …"
msgstr "nasty jealousy …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.10"
msgid "pāpikā icchā abhibhuyya iriyati."
msgstr "or corrupt wishes master them and keep going."

msgctxt "an10.23:7.11"
msgid "So evamassa veditabbo:"
msgstr "You should know of them:"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.12"
msgid ""
"‘nāyamāyasmā tathā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ "
"āyasmantaṃ lobho abhibhuyya iriyati;"
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable does not have the understanding that would eliminate greed, "
"so greed masters them and keeps going."

msgctxt "an10.23:7.13"
msgid "nāyamāyasmā tathā pajānāti yathā pajānato doso na hoti …"
msgstr "They don’t have the understanding that would eliminate hate …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.14"
msgid "moho …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.15"
msgid "kodho …"
msgstr "anger …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.16"
msgid "upanāho …"
msgstr "hostility …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.17"
msgid "makkho …"
msgstr "offensiveness …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.18"
msgid "paḷāso …"
msgstr "contempt …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.19"
msgid "macchariyaṃ …"
msgstr "stinginess …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.20"
msgid "pāpikā issā …"
msgstr "nasty jealousy …"

msgctxt "an10.23:7.21"
msgid ""
"pāpikā icchā na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ pāpikā icchā abhibhuyya "
"iriyatī’ti."
msgstr "or corrupt wishes, so corrupt wishes master them and keep going.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an10.23:8.1"
msgid "Tañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuṃ lobho nābhibhuyya iriyati, "
msgstr "Suppose that greed does not master that mendicant and keep going. "

msgctxt "an10.23:8.2"
msgid "doso …"
msgstr "Or that hate …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.3"
msgid "moho …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.4"
msgid "kodho …"
msgstr "anger …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.5"
msgid "upanāho …"
msgstr "hostility …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.6"
msgid "makkho …"
msgstr "offensiveness …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.7"
msgid "paḷāso …"
msgstr "contempt …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.8"
msgid "macchariyaṃ …"
msgstr "stinginess …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.9"
msgid "pāpikā issā …"
msgstr "nasty jealousy …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.10"
msgid "pāpikā icchā nābhibhuyya iriyati, "
msgstr "or corrupt wishes don’t master that mendicant and keep going. "

msgctxt "an10.23:8.11"
msgid "so evamassa veditabbo:"
msgstr "You should know of them:"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.12"
msgid ""
"‘tathā ayamāyasmā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ "
"āyasmantaṃ lobho nābhibhuyya iriyati;"
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable has the understanding that eliminates greed, so greed doesn’"
"t master them and keep going."

msgctxt "an10.23:8.13"
msgid "tathā ayamāyasmā pajānāti yathā pajānato doso na hoti …"
msgstr "They have the understanding that eliminates hate …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.14"
msgid "moho …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.15"
msgid "kodho …"
msgstr "anger …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.16"
msgid "upanāho …"
msgstr "hostility …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.17"
msgid "makkho …"
msgstr "offensiveness …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.18"
msgid "paḷāso …"
msgstr "contempt …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.19"
msgid "macchariyaṃ …"
msgstr "stinginess …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.20"
msgid "pāpikā issā …"
msgstr "nasty jealousy …"

msgctxt "an10.23:8.21"
msgid ""
"pāpikā icchā na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ pāpikā icchā nābhibhuyya "
"iriyatī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"and corrupt wishes, so corrupt wishes don’t master them and keep going.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.23:8.22"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
